<br>
But the fact is, as others have said, your level in relation to the mob often times is the biggest factor.  And by the time you spend a level or five in a dungeon that &quot;relationship&quot; shifts dramatically.  Who knows if it was your spell that allowed you to single pull or the fact that you gained another level since the last time you tried?  <br>
